    "rowsha": "24F179t5KuR2fwjj+ksg3KKNbB7WRdR8vIo4kf92mMs=",
    "originContent": "After downloading and unpacking the TidalSwift.zip, move the app to the Applications folder. Because the app is unsigned (I refuse to give current Apple money), you need to explicitly allow the app after the first start in the Privacy system settings. Alternatively, you can execute this:",
